title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 10 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 10 2022
description:
Clay and Buck contemplate the disastrous Democrat policies that have incentivized homelessness and crime. They play for us the words of an entitled drug dealer who asks why he should pay rent when he's so well-subsidized by benefits from San Francisco. Dems have ruined these cities ("hellscapes," as Buck calls them) with their idiotic ideas. When will it end? Rep. Michael Waltz joins C&B to discuss NBC spiking his Olympic genocide ad, made with Enes Kanter Freedom. NBC called for so many changes, including not mentioning corporate names, that it was a "nonrejection rejection."
